  "prompt": "When is the CA-CPT exam held?",
  "response": "The CA-CPT (Common Proficiency Test) is now known as the CA Foundation exam. The CA Foundation exam is typically conducted by the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) twice a year, in May and November. However, the exact dates can vary each year, so it's essential to check ICAI's official website or contact them directly for the most up-to-date information regarding exam schedules and registration deadlines.",
